      "content": "sometimes i look in the mirror and i dont even recognize the person looking back. not because i look different, but because it feels like the person who actually mattered... the one with the dreams and the spark... died a long time ago. i'm just going through the motions now. like a ghost inhabiting a body that doesn't belong to me anymore.",
